high_descs: Pick up the blue vase on the dining table.
Bring the blue vase to the safe on the floor.
Put the vase in the safe on the floor.

high_descs: Turn to the right and go around the table to where the blue disk is.
Pick up the blue disk that is on the table.
Turn around and with the blue disk go to the safe.
Open the safe.  Put the blue disk inside and close the safe.
anns.task_desc: Put the disk in the safe.

high_descs: Turn right, walk around the table, to the other side of the table
Grab the blue bottle on the table
Turn around, walk past the door, turn right, walk to the corner
Put the blue bottle in the white box on the floor
anns.task_desc: Move the blue bottle on the table to the white box on the floor
